'''ALGOL W'''，一種[[程式語言|程式語言]]，為[[ALGOL|ALGOL]]家族的一份子。它基於[[尼克勞斯·維爾特|尼克勞斯·維爾特]]與[[東尼·霍爾|東尼·霍爾]]在[[IFIP_Working_Group_2.1|IFIP Working Group 2.1]]提出的 {{en-link|ALGOL X|ALGOL X}}草案而設計，希望能作為[[ALGOL_60|ALGOL 60]]的後繼者<ref name="wirth">[http://portal.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=365696.365702 Niklaus Wirth & C. A. R Hoare (1966)] A contribution to the development of ALGOL. Communications of the ACM, Vol.9, pp. 413–432</ref>。經過小幅度的修改<ref>[http://portal.acm.org/citation.cfm?doid=1061073.1061079 Niklaus Wirth (1966)], ''Additional notes on "A Contribution to the Development of ALGOL"'', ALGOL Bulletin, Number 24 pp. 13 - 17.</ref>，在[[史丹福大學|史丹福大學]]，[[尼克勞斯·維爾特|尼克勞斯·維爾特]]利用[[IBM/360|IBM/360]]機器，實作出第一版的ALGOL W<ref name="standford">[http://www-db.stanford.edu/TR/CS-TR-68-89.html Stanford Computer Science Department Technical Report CS-TR-68-89] {{Wayback|url=http://www-db.stanford.edu/TR/CS-TR-68-89.html |date=20060213101159 }} (Various documents for Stanford University's 1972 implementation of ALGOL W; this report includes the ''ALGOL W Language Description''.)</ref>
。

它的[[編譯器|編譯器]]是用[[尼克勞斯·維爾特|尼克勞斯·維爾特]]所設計的[[PL360|PL360]]組語所寫成<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://bitsavers.trailing-edge.com/pdf/stanford/cs_techReports/STAN-CS-71-215_PL360_Revised_A_Programming_Language_For_The_IBM_360_May71.pdf |title=PL360(REVISED) A PROGRAMMING LANGUAGE FOR THE IBM 360. |accessdate=2020-05-16 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304073807/http://bitsavers.trailing-edge.com/pdf/stanford/cs_techReports/STAN-CS-71-215_PL360_Revised_A_Programming_Language_For_The_IBM_360_May71.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 例子 ==

下面例子展示ALGOL W的[[记录|记录]]类型设施：

<syntaxhighlight lang="pascal">
RECORD PERSON (
    STRING(20) NAME; 
    INTEGER AGE; 
    LOGICAL MALE; 
    REFERENCE(PERSON) FATHER, MOTHER, YOUNGESTOFFSPRING, ELDERSIBLING
);

REFERENCE(PERSON) PROCEDURE YOUNGESTUNCLE (REFERENCE(PERSON) R);
    BEGIN
        REFERENCE(PERSON) P, M;
        P := YOUNGESTOFFSPRING(FATHER(FATHER(R)));
        WHILE (P ¬= NULL) AND (¬ MALE(P)) OR (P = FATHER(R)) DO
            P := ELDERSIBLING(P);
        M := YOUNGESTOFFSPRING(MOTHER(MOTHER(R)));
        WHILE (M ¬= NULL) AND (¬ MALE(M)) DO
            M := ELDERSIBLING(M);
        IF P = NULL THEN 
            M 
        ELSE IF M = NULL THEN 
            P 
        ELSE 
            IF AGE(P) < AGE(M) THEN P ELSE M
    END
</syntaxhighlight>

